This product includes software developed by Muninn / Crowork.

The core speech-act gate is a generalization of a single-domain ingest gate
that has been running in production in the Muninn personal-assistant relay
since 2026-06-05 (originally guarding menstrual-cycle reports in EN+HE; this
release is domain-agnostic and covers EN / HE / RU / RO).

The Beta(2,2) trust model and decay scanner are described in the Muninn
Memory OS design (docs/plans/2026-06-05-muninn-memory-os.md).
